      <cop_rqr_nm>§412.25(a)(13)</cop_rqr_nm>
      <cop_tx>(13) As of the first day of the first cost reporting period for which all other exclusion requirements are met, the unit is fully equipped and staffed and is capable of providing hospital inpatient psychiatric or rehabilitation care regardless of whether there are any inpatients in the unit on that date.</cop_tx>
      <COMMENT>See Appendix B of the CAMCAH.</COMMENT>
