    <COP_ELE>
      <cop_rqr_nm>§412.25(c)</cop_rqr_nm>
      <cop_tx>(c) Changes in the status of hospital units. For purposes of exclusions from the prospective payment systems under this section, the status of each hospital unit (excluded or not excluded) is determined as specified in paragraphs (c)(1) and (c)(2) of this section.</cop_tx>
      <COMMENT>See Appendix B of the CAMCAH.</COMMENT>
    </COP_ELE>
    <COP_ELE>
      <cop_rqr_nm>§412.25(c)(1)</cop_rqr_nm>
      <cop_tx>(1) The status of a hospital unit may be changed from not excluded to excluded only at the start of the cost reporting period. If a unit is added to a hospital after the start of a cost reporting period, it cannot be excluded from the prospective payment systems before the start of a hospital’s next cost reporting period.</cop_tx>
      <COMMENT>See Appendix B of the CAMCAH.</COMMENT>
      <TAG>
        <TAG_NM>C-0519</TAG_NM>
        <TAG_HDG>Changes in the status of hospital units</TAG_HDG>
      </TAG>
