      <cop_rqr_nm>§412.25(c)(1)</cop_rqr_nm>
      <cop_tx>(1) The status of a hospital unit may be changed from not excluded to excluded only at the start of the cost reporting period. If a unit is added to a hospital after the start of a cost reporting period, it cannot be excluded from the prospective payment systems before the start of a hospital’s next cost reporting period.</cop_tx>
