      <cop_tx>(i) In the case of a unit excluded from the prospective payment systems for the most recent cost reporting period beginning before October 1, 1997, the unit’s number of State-licensed and Medicare-certified beds, including those at the satellite facility, does not exceed the unit’s number of State-licensed and Medicare-certified beds on the last day of the unit’s last cost reporting period beginning before October 1, 1997.</cop_tx>
