      <cop_tx>(f) Changes in classification of hospital units. For purposes of exclusions from the prospective payment system under this section, the classification of a hospital unit is effective for the unit’s entire cost reporting period. Any change in the classification of a hospital unit is made only at the start of a cost reporting period.</cop_tx>
